&lt;p&gt;Thought Iâ€™d try the &lt;a href=&#34;https://atom.io&#34;&gt;Atom Editor&lt;/a&gt; on my &lt;a href=&#34;http://opensuse.org&#34;&gt;openSUSE&lt;/a&gt; Tumbleweed install.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
